WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.933 --> 00:00:01.700
She’s having an allergic reaction

2
00:00:02.733 --> 00:00:04.733
Duan Xiao Jian put peanut powder in my water

3
00:00:07.566 --> 00:00:08.466
Don’t go

4
00:00:08.966 --> 00:00:10.300
He’s downstairs watching closely

5
00:00:10.766 --> 00:00:12.300
Let him watch then

6
00:00:12.333 --> 00:00:13.233
I’m Ye Qi Luo now

7
00:00:13.366 --> 00:00:15.066
Even if God himself shows up, so what?

8
00:00:15.766 --> 00:00:16.966
Lao Jin went to get the medicine

9
00:00:17.600 --> 00:00:18.733
He’ll be back soon

10
00:00:19.066 --> 00:00:19.866
Ye Ci

11
00:00:20.066 --> 00:00:21.333
Whatever you do, the bottom line is

12
00:00:21.366 --> 00:00:22.633
don’t gamble with your life

13
00:00:23.400 --> 00:00:24.733
Then what can I do?

14
00:00:26.000 --> 00:00:27.300
Just throw away all my past efforts?

15
00:00:29.166 --> 00:00:29.933
There’s no time

16
00:00:30.566 --> 00:00:31.333
Open your mouth

17
00:00:44.366 --> 00:00:45.433
For revenge,

18
00:00:45.466 --> 00:00:46.333
you’re even willing to risk your life

19
00:00:46.600 --> 00:00:47.533
How foolish is that?

20
00:01:09.066 --> 00:01:09.933
How is she?

21
00:01:11.900 --> 00:01:13.066
No reaction at all

22
00:01:13.533 --> 00:01:14.500
And no trip to the hospital

23
00:01:15.566 --> 00:01:16.733
I told you

24
00:01:17.000 --> 00:01:18.500
She can’t be Ye Ci

25
00:01:23.966 --> 00:01:24.733
What are you looking at?

26
00:01:26.400 --> 00:01:27.633
Do you think I look good

27
00:01:27.666 --> 00:01:28.500
in this wedding dress?

28
00:01:29.700 --> 00:01:30.966
Why are you suddenly looking at wedding dresses?

29
00:01:31.200 --> 00:01:32.533
I had someone check

30
00:01:32.966 --> 00:01:33.633
The 20th of this month

31
00:01:33.666 --> 00:01:34.900
is a good day

32
00:01:36.166 --> 00:01:36.966
Our wedding

33
00:01:37.000 --> 00:01:38.566
will be held on the 20th of this month

34
00:01:43.000 --> 00:01:45.133
Isn’t that a bit sudden?

35
00:01:46.933 --> 00:01:47.833
What do you mean by that?
